  "title": "🌙 NIGHT CASHIERS 💳 @ BUGIS | Up to $2.6k++| NO EXPERIENCES NEEDED",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>🌙 NIGHT CASHIERS 💳 @ BUGIS | Up to $2.6k++| NO EXPERIENCES NEEDED</strong></u></p><p>📍Location: Bugis </p><p>💰Salary: $2,400-$2,600 + Night shift allowance!! </p><p>🗓️Working days:  </p><p>44h a week, 6 days  </p><p>🕑Shift hours:   </p><p>6.30pm-3.30am </p><p>Job role: </p><ul><li><p>Handle <strong>customer check-ins and check-outs</strong>, room allocation, billing, and <strong>cashless/cash transactions</strong> accurately and efficiently. </p></li><li><p>Provide <strong>friendly customer service</strong>, manage inquiries, and resolve basic issues to ensure a positive guest experience. </p></li><li><p>Coordinate with service crew and operations staff to ensure smooth room turnover and <strong>timely service</strong> during peak hours. </p></li><li><p>Maintain cashier counter cleanliness, ensure accurate cash handling, and follow company SOPs and security procedures. </p></li></ul><p>Requirements:  </p><ul><li><p>Able to work night shifts </p></li></ul><p>📥Interested? Send us your resume at 8032 2021 or email: admin@crew.sg </p><p>Please include your availability, notice period and expected salary. </p><p>*<em>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified</em> </p><p>Megan Tan </p><p>Outsourcing Team </p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet </p><p>EA 24C2435 </p>",
